description:
The Best and Most Secret App to keep your photos and videos safe for iPhone/iPad/iPod touch. Download NOW!

This app used for hide your private photo, video and other secret files behind a calculator.

What everyone can see is just an ordinary calculator. Until you type in your secret passcode it became a private storage app in which you can hide your most secret photos, videos, notes, and more.


Features:
· Photo & Video Management:
You can add/download your private photos & videos into secret calculator, we provides many ways:
- Add your secret photo/video from Camera Roll;
- Add your secret photo/video from iTunes File Sharing Sync;
- Download your secret photo/video from Cloud Drive(Dropbox and Google Drive) ;

· Photo & Video Security:
Hide your private photos & videos disguised as a calculator app.
- You can Lock/unlock the app with password;
- You can easy to access photo & video privacy with only one password lock;
- Reset your password if you need.

· Other features:
Use as a normal calculator app;
- Add your private notes and contacts in the app;
- Manage all your private files which iOS support;
- View all your private photos & media files which iOS suport format  eg. Image: png,jpg,jpeg, audio & video: mov, mp4, m4v, 3gp, mp3 and documents:doc, xls, ppt, pdf, zip...
- Build in private web browser for search photo/video privately.

Note:
• All of your data in this app is stored only in your device. We don't access or store your privacy.

Heart rate monitors (HRMs) can be immensely beneficial if you know how to use the information they collect.

Exercise has very different effects on the body depending on how high you push your heart rate and for how long. Training intelligently means using heart rate data to guide your workouts. Sometimes you might want to keep your heart rate relatively low to burn fat or pace yourself for a longer workout, whereas other times you want to push it higher for different health benefits, like building stamina.

Another reason to own a HRM is to keep an eye on your resting heart rate with a device that will automatically record it for you.

The app integrated with the Health app to:
- Retrive your age and calculate max Heart Rate;
- Monitor current Heart Rate;
- Start exercises like walking, running, cycling and etc;
